{"_id":"NDBhZmIwZTg1NTM1","name":"Roll20 Note about Rollable Tokens","content":"<section class=\"secret\">The tokens for @Actor[MDY4MzkwMzM3OTA5]{Aarakocra}, @Actor[ODYwMTFlZGY3N2Q1]{Arcanaloth}, @Actor[NmU4Yzc1ODIzMmE4]{Azaka Stormfang}, @Actor[YTVkNGVlNTBmMGYy]{Eku}, @Actor[BP2X19wu7eCkPDDa]{Captain Elok Jaharwon}, @Actor[N2FkYWM4YjFhNTc3]{Goblin}, @Actor[Yjc0NGFmZDIwZTYx]{Fenthaza}, @Actor[MWYxNWJiZWY2YWRm]{Nanny Pu'pu}, @Actor[YTZkYTg4ZjMxMzZm]{Ras Nsi}, @Actor[ZjZhY2I4ODA2ZTUx]{Mister Threadneedle}, @Actor[OTUzY2QzMWQxY2My]{Valindra Shadowmantle}, @Actor[MDBiZjAwNTYxNDZi]{Wereboar}, @Actor[OTE3ZjY5ZWQxODcz]{Weretiger}, @Actor[YzBiMDQ3NzM1YTEz]{Yuan-ti Abomination}, @Actor[Mzk0NDgxZGM4M2Mz]{Yuan-ti Malison Type 1}, @Actor[ODY0MTlhOTMyYTZi]{Yuan-ti Malison Type 2}, @Actor[ZTQ0MzFjYjE2NDdj]{Yuan-ti Malison Type 3}, @Actor[ZDZjOTA0MDMyYjY3]{Yuan-ti Malison Type 4}, @Actor[MzJhNDVlZDMyOTky]{Yuan-ti Malison Type 5}, @Actor[NjViN2FjNTdmYTcw]{Yuan-ti Nightmare Speaker}, @Actor[MTRkNzBhNTY4YjEx]{Yuan-ti Priest} are multi-sided rollable table tokens. Each side of one of these tokens is a different form for the creature. To swap between the different sides, right click on one of these tokens and choose Multi-Sided -&gt; Choose Side.</section>","img":null,"folder":"ZjkyYzY1ODNlNWYy","sort":40000,"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{"R20Converter":{"handout-order":4,"handout-archived":false}}}
