{"_id":"YjZjNzQzM2JlYmZk","name":"Wand of Secrets","permission":{"default":0},"folder":"OGVmYWE2MTQ5YTYw","flags":{"R20Converter":{"handout-order":50,"handout-archived":false}},"sort":500000,"entryTime":0,"content":"<h3>Wand of Secrets</h3><em>Wand, uncommon</em><br><br>The wand has 3 charges. While holding it. you can use an action to expend 1 of its charges, and if a secret door or trap is within 30 feet of you, the wand pulses and points at the one nearest to you. The wand regains 1d3 expended charges daily at dawn.<br>","img":"worlds/toa/journal/magic-items/wand-of-secrets/avatar.webp"}
