{"_id":"Yjg0OGZjZTI3ZWRh","name":"Oil of Sharpness","permission":{"default":0},"folder":"OGVmYWE2MTQ5YTYw","flags":{"R20Converter":{"handout-order":28,"handout-archived":false}},"sort":280000,"entryTime":0,"content":"<h4>Oil of Sharpness</h4><em>Potion, very rare</em><br><br>This clear, gelatinous oil sparkles with tiny, ultrathin silver shards. The oil can coat one slashing or piercing weapon or up to 5 pieces of slashing or piercing ammunition. Applying the oil takes 1 minute. For 1 hour, the coated item is magical and has a +3 bonus to attack and damage rolls.<br><br>","img":""}
