{"_id":"ZTA5Yzk5NGM0ODc3","name":"I'jin's Spirit Handout","permission":{"default":0},"folder":"MjBlNjZiYmY0MjMx","flags":{"R20Converter":{"handout-order":0,"handout-archived":false}},"sort":0,"entryTime":0,"content":"<h2>I'jin</h2><em>(pronounced EYE-jin)</em><br>I'jin, the Almiraj, is fickle and unpredictable.<br><br><h3>Flaw</h3>While inhabited by I'jin, you gain the following flaw, which overrides any opposing flaw: \"I never stick to a plan.\"<br><br><h3>Power</h3>While I'jin inhabits you, your Dexterity score becomes 23 unless it is already higher.<br>","img":"worlds/toa/journal/chapter-5-3a-tomb-of-the-nine-gods/chapter-5-3a-player-handouts/trickster-gods-of-omu-handouts/i-27jin-27s-spirit-handout/avatar.webp"}
