title-inner\">Handout 8: River Mist and Flask of Wine</span></span> <p></p><div class=\"float-clear\"></div><div><div class=\"rd__wrp-image relative\">\n\t\t\t<a href=\"worlds/toa/img/adventure/toa/046-ph08.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">\n\t\t\t\t<img class=\"rd__image\" src=\"worlds/toa/img/adventure/toa/046-ph08.jpg\" />\n\t\t\t</a>\n\t\t</div></div><p></p></div><div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--1\"><span class=\"rd__h rd__h--1\" data-title-index=\"6046\"> <span class=\"entry-title-inner\">Handout 9: Salida</span></span> <p></p><div class=\"float-clear\"></div><div><div class=\"rd__wrp-image relative\">\n\t\t\t<a href=\"worlds/toa/img/adventure/toa/047-ph09.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">\n\t\t\t\t<img class=\"rd__image\" src=\"worlds/toa/img/adventure/toa/047-ph09.jpg\" />\n\t\t\t</a>\n\t\t</div></div><p></p></div><div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--1\"><span class=\"rd__h rd__h--1\" data-title-index=\"6047\"> <span class=\"entry-title-inner\">Handout 10: Shago</span></span> <p></p><div class=\"float-clear\"></div><div><div class=\"rd__wrp-image relative\">\n\t\t\t<a href=\"worlds/toa/img/adventure/toa/048-ph10.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">\n\t\t\t\t<img class=\"rd__image\" src=\"worlds/toa/img/adventure/toa/048-ph10.jpg\" />\n\t\t\t</a>\n\t\t</div></div><p></p></div></div><hr class=\"rd__hr rd__hr--section\" /><div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--0\"><span class=\"rd__h rd__h--0\" data-title-index=\"6048\"> <span class=\"entry-title-inner\">Handout 11: Puzzle Cubes</span></span> <p></p><div class=\"float-clear\"></div><div><div class=\"rd__wrp-image relative\">\n\t\t\t<a href=\"worlds/toa/img/adventure/toa/049-ph11.png\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">\n\t\t\t\t<img class=\"rd__image\" src=\"worlds/toa/img/adventure/toa/049-ph11.png\" />\n\t\t\t</a>\n\t\t</div></div><p></p></div><hr class=\"rd__hr rd__hr--section\" /><div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--0\"><span class=\"rd__h rd__h--0\" data-title-index=\"6049\"> <span class=\"entry-title-inner\">Handout 12: Players' Map of Omu</span></span> <p></p><div class=\"float-clear\"></div><div><div class=\"rd__wrp-image relative\">\n\t\t\t<a href=\"worlds/toa/img/adventure/toa/050-ph12.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">\n\t\t\t\t<img class=\"rd__image\" src=\"worlds/toa/img/adventure/toa/050-ph12.jpg\" />\n\t\t\t</a>\n\t\t</div></div><p></p></div><hr class=\"rd__hr rd__hr--section\" /><div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--0\"><span class=\"rd__h rd__h--0\" data-title-index=\"6050\"> <span class=\"entry-title-inner\">Handout 13: Lord Brixton's Letter</span></span> <p></p><div class=\"float-clear\"></div><div><div class=\"rd__wrp-image relative\">\n\t\t\t<a href=\"worlds/toa/img/adventure/toa/051-ph13.png\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">\n\t\t\t\t<img class=\"rd__image\" src=\"worlds/toa/img/adventure/toa/051-ph13.png\" />\n\t\t\t</a>\n\t\t</div></div><p></p></div><hr class=\"rd__hr rd__hr--section\" /><div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--0\"><span class=\"rd__h rd__h--0\" data-title-index=\"6051\"> <span class=\"entry-title-inner\">Handout 14: I'jin's Puzzle Floor</span></span> <p></p><div class=\"float-clear\"></div><div><div class=\"rd__wrp-image relative\">\n\t\t\t<a href=\"worlds/toa/img/adventure/toa/052-ph14.png\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">\n\t\t\t\t<img class=\"rd__image\" src=\"worlds/toa/img/adventure/toa/052-ph14.png\" />\n\t\t\t</a>\n\t\t</div></div><p></p></div><hr class=\"rd__hr rd__hr--section\" /><div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--0\"><span class=\"rd__h rd__h--0\" data-title-index=\"6052\"> <span class=\"entry-title-inner\">Handout 15: Papazotl's Riddle</span></span> <p></p><div class=\"float-clear\"></div><div><div class=\"rd__wrp-image relative\">\n\t\t\t<a href=\"worlds/toa/img/adventure/toa/053-ph15.png\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">\n\t\t\t\t<img class=\"rd__image\" src=\"worlds/toa/img/adventure/toa/053-ph15.png\" />\n\t\t\t</a>\n\t\t</div></div><p></p></div><hr class=\"rd